args {set color [randcolor]; set word [join $args " "] ;set ret [list]; set dots [string repeat "." [expr {[string length $word]/5 + 2}] ] ;lappend ret "[pyramid $dots]" ;  lappend ret "[center "| [string repeat " " [string length $word]] |" [expr {[string length $dots]*9}]]"; lappend ret [center "| $word |" [expr {[string length $dots]*9}]]; join $ret \n; regsub "|" $ret "$color|[color]"}
